1959 WHITE BURGUNDIES

Here are the great, full bodied 1959 white wines of Burgundy of much depth and character, similar to the 1947s, and entirely remarkable. Practically all of these are here in bottle, quite ready to drink, and proud heralds of the new heights achieved by an outstanding vintage year.
